      <section id="id1170713691683">
        <title>Making</title>
        <para id="id1170705041746">Steps for making the product _______________through a simple process flow chart.</para>
        <para id="id1170703569167">The functions of a process flow chart are:</para>
        <list id="id3895187" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>to separate actions in a process;</item>
          <item>to arrange the different actions in a logical order.</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id2191321">Every type of activity is described by a frame or block with a specific shape.</para>
        <para id="id1170705039554"> Write the different stages by making sentences with each action, material and tool that youâ€™ve used. Use only one action in a frame.</para>
